# Graphify's graph/cache is derived and machine-local. Curated work memory is
# retained so decisions and corrections survive a clone.
graphify-out/*
!graphify-out/memory/
!graphify-out/memory/*.md
!graphify-out/reflections/
!graphify-out/reflections/LESSONS.md

